ANU.name: Steven Welsh
ANU.biography: After attending the ANU as an exchange student in 2015-2016, Steven returned to the ANU in 2018 to commence working towards his PhD in the field of organometallic and coordination chemistry under the supervision of Prof. Tony Hill. Currently, his work revolves around expanding the field of Early Transition Metal Poly(methimazolyl)borate Complexes.
